OL,5, Young shoppers risk building up debts  
OL,6, by borrowing money to make buy now pay 
OL,7, later repayments, Citizens Advice says.
OL,9,FHalf of 18 to 34-year-olds used        
OL,10,Fdifferent types of credit - such as    
OL,11,Fcredit cards or borrowing from family -
OL,12,Fto make the payments, it said.         
OL,14,FAlthough the results were drawn from a 
OL,15,Fsurvey, the charity said the answers   
OL,16,Fhighlighted the issue of people relying
OL,17,Fon one debt to cover another.          
OL,19,FChanges are being made that make some  
OL,20,Fof these debts clearer to lenders.     
